sorcer.util

Class CmdFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • sorcer.util.CmdFactory

  • public abstract class CmdFactory
extends Object
    An abstract factory for all GApp commands provided by a factory ..CmdProvider. Real factories called command providers are subclasses of this class.
